    "The GLT is especially important in probing the null point near 3.4 Gλ.",
    "This is proven by the increased number of Top Set images for the trained methods and the cleaner reconstruction of the ring-like morphology compared to bands 1 and 2.",
    "On the April 25 data, DIFMAP, eht-imaging, and SMILI struggled to produce a significant number of Top Set imagesnone of the methods could produce Top Set images for bands 1 and 2.",
    "The Bayesian methods also struggle to produce a ring-like morphology for data taken on this day.",
    "This performance issue is mainly due to a lack of data from LMT on this day."
